h1 Login
p
  form(role="form", ng-submit="login()")
    pre(ng-show="!!message") {{ message | json }}
    ui-textbox(label="Username", value="userName", disabled="busy")
    ui-password(label="Password", value="password", disabled="busy")
    input.btn.btn-primary(type="submit", value="Login", ng-disabled="busy")
p
  | You have no account yet? Then <a ng-href="/register">Register</a> now. It's free!
